      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://alltypesofdogs.org/?p=1307</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;As you may know, Labradors were originally gun dogs, picked specifically for their retrieving abilities. Of course, Labradors can do much more than that but that was their original purpose. These clever dogs can undertake most dog tasks with ease.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Regardless, nowadays they are more house-pets, less gun dogs, however they are still used for that by some people. The Labrador is the most popular dog in the United States, and he is in the top 5 in several other major countries. Now you would [...] &lt;strong&gt;More about:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href="http://alltypesofdogs.org/overview-on-labrador-retrievers-the-most-popular-dogs.html"&gt;Overview on Labrador Retrievers, The Most Popular Dogs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/all-types-of-dogs-realm/All_Types_Of_Dogs_Realm-Overview_on_Labrador_Retrievers_The_Most_Popular_Dogs.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
